'''Tamaḍunt''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tsrɣint]] : مرض) tga kullu man usnulfu nɣ assnfl illan g [[Tadusi|tdusi]] n ufgan nɣ n kra n [[Amaddar|umaddar]] yaḍni, assnfl ad iẓḍaṛ ad ig afggan (izdi d [[Tafgga n ufgan|tfgga]]) nɣ animan (izdi d [[iman]]).

Tamaḍunt tmzaray f waṭṭan (aṭṭan). Iɣ ar nsawal f waṭṭan at ar nsawal f ufsar (tazzla n ufsar) n kra n tmaḍunt g kra n tmazirt.

